title: Thermodynamic properties of Aluminum — alProp
text: dataset contains temperature-dependent thermodynamic properties Aluminum 99.99% purity. contains temperature, density, cp, thermal conductivity, thermal expansion coefficient.

title: Thermodynamic properties of Aluminum — alProp
text: dataframe 5 variables 599 observations. T/K temperature rho/(kg/m3) density cp/(J/(kg.K)) isobaric specific heat K/(W/(m.K)) thermal conductivity alpha_thermal/(1/K) thermal expansion coefficient
